properties.description: A beautiful bungalow in the Bayview area with some fantastic features! The freshly stained wooden floors and open kitchen concept add a modern touch, while the woodwork throughout the house creates a warm and inviting atmosphere. The window seats and stained glass in the living room and dining area are likely stunning architectural details that enhance the overall charm of the home. Moving to the second floor to a brighter modern Level it has office space and two additional bedroom. It also has the primary master room with attached full bathroom is undoubtedly a luxurious feature, providing a private and comfortable retreat within the home. This property has such character and thoughtful design elements often appeal to those who appreciate a blend of classic and modern aesthetics.
properties.location: Petts Wood Road, Petts Wood, Orpington

properties.description: Old world charm meets modern conveniences with this 5 bed, 2 bath Bay View bungalow! Imagine lounging on the inviting front porch during warmer months & welcoming guests in through the stunning stained-glass door. Gorgeous hardwood floors, natural woodwork & tall baseboards for that right-at-home feel! Prepare your next culinary masterpiece in the updated kitchen, to be served in the formal dining room w/ built-ins as you host your next dinner party. Split bedroom layout with 2 up & 2 down means potential to use a bedroom as a home office or walk-in closet! Dry & clean lower level with charming rec room expands your living space. Private & fully-fenced backyard with patio is great for entertaining or playing fetch with Fido. No lack of parking here-- 2 car detached garage. Welcome home!

Welcome home! This well cared for 3-bedroom, 1.5-bath single-family home is a haven nestled between the scenic beauty of Humboldt Park and the recreational allure of Emigh Playfield. Boasting almost instant freeway access, this residence is not just a home; it's a gateway to convenience. Imagine strolling to nearby shops, restaurants, and the library, or taking a short drive to the airport and the picturesque Lake Michigan. The small mudroom greets you, offering a perfect spot for hanging jackets and kicking off shoes. Also, please feel free to indulge in the three-season room ideal for your morning coffee retreat or spacious enough to house a hot tub. Large side yard, complemented by a 2.5-car garage with additional parking in the rear. Enjoy all the benefits of the Bayview Community.

Add this beautiful Bay View duplex to your portfolio and you won't be disappointed. Two 1200 sq foot 2 bed/ 1 bath units are both fully occupied through 2024. Exuding old world charm, each unit features large kitchens and baths, high ceilings, and gorgeous hardwood floors. A cozy yard invites gardening projects and a 1.5 car garage plus a slab provide easy parking. Tenants are responsible for all utilities plus lawn and snow care. The unfinished third floor provides extra storage or potential to expand. Drain tile has been replaced and the basement has been beamed for peace of mind. Newer paint, windows, hot water heaters, and AC units plus term leases and established, professional management mean this one is set and forget for any investor.

$113K+ of Gross Rent on the books for 2023! Amazing investment or beach home with DIRECT WALK-UP ACCESS TO THE BEACH! This stylishly decorated, fully furnished condo is centrally located on the Gulf side of the beautiful AZURE Condominium resort. Prime location on the ground floor with easy access to the pool area and the sugar-sand beaches just beyond make this unit one of the most desirable rentals in the complex. Quick and convenient access to the covered parking garage and no need for stairs or elevators. A rare find perfect for a second home, primary residence or a lucrative investment property. The condo is a phenomenal vacation rental with consistently high gross rental numbers year over year. The unit features tile throughout (no carpet). Water heater and dishwasher replaced in Dec. 2021. 9 Ft ceilings throughout and an open floor plan create a spacious, inviting atmosphere. Two King bedrooms and a third spacious bedroom with a Queen and Twin, as well as a Queen-sized sleeper sofa in the living room. Huge master bathroom with separate shower and garden tub. Higher occupancy capacity than higher floor units. Per the Azure condominium regulations and fire code restrictions ground floor units are allowed to sleep more occupants than similar units on higher floors. Unit 113 is allowed 10 occupants. The Azure complex features two pools (one seasonally heated), two large hot tubs, covered parking garage and code gate access, lush tropical landscaping, newly updated beach walkway, fully equipped exercise room and outdoor grills available to owners and guests. Buyer to verify all information.
properties.location: 1150 Santa Rosa Blvd Unit 113, Fort Walton Beach, FL 32548

properties.description: Flip flops and bathing suits are required; this is your chance to own the beach life! Centrally located to the stunning emerald waters of Navarre Beach and Santa Rosa Sound (Deeded Access), you have the best of both worlds. Dip your toes in the sugar sand, sunbathe, and play in the Gulf of Mexico, or grab your favorite watercraft and hit the calm waters of the sound. This recently renovated, furnished, two-bedroom, two-bath condo is ready for a new owner. For all the investors out there, Sugar Dunes can be rented on a short-term basis. The main living area is an open-floor concept, White-washed wood tongue and groove ceilings, upgraded lighting, and wood-like tile floorsplenty of room to relax or entertain without feeling cramped for space. Enjoy your view of the Santa Rosa Sound as you cook in the newly renovated kitchen offering new cabinetry with pull-out shelving, accented tile backsplash, and new appliances. The master bedroom offers plenty of space to stretch out after a fun-filled day at the beach. The master ensuite has recently been renovated with new cabinets, upgraded lighting, and a tiled shower. The second bedroom offers bunk beds, a full-sized bed on the lower bunk a twin up top. Hurricane shutters throughout the unit. Did I mention that Navarre Beach is golf cart friendly from Navarre Marine Park to the National Sea Shore? Own and store your recreational items in your garage. Sugar Dunes is dog-friendly for owners up to 25 pounds. HVAC 2020, Roof 2021, Water heater 2017, Gutters replaced 2021, New Hardie board on gables 2021, Stucco repainted 2021, Rear balconies replaced 2021, Pilings reinforced 2021, Privacy fence installed 2021
properties.location: 1448 Tina Dr Apt 224, Navarre Beach, FL 32566

properties.description: Fractional Ownership! Share G for sale. Enjoy renowned views overlooking Destin Harbor, East Pass, and the Gulf of Mexico from your expansive balcony. Owners of the luxury fractional shares at Emerald Grande experience a unique vacation lifestyle. Owners can enjoy room service, onsite Spa and Fitness Center, garage parking, and much more. Fractional ownership allows you to purchase only what you use and removes the legwork of finding other buyers to partner with you and provides a hassle free ownership. At Emerald Grande, every imaginable activity awaits you, just steps from HarborWalk Village
properties.location: 10 Harbor Blvd Unit E506G, Destin, FL 32541

properties.description: Ready now! Ashton ranch plan in Flying Horse. 5 bedroom, 4.5 bath home, 3 car garage home. Farmhouse style exterior. Walk-in from insulated 3 car garage into a large laundry room with lots of cabinets and laundry sink. Main level showcases bright and airy great room with vaulted ceilings and fireplace. Formal dining room. Gourmet layout kitchen features smoke gray finished maple cabinets, Calacatta Quartz countertops, large island, brushed gold faucet and hardware, and Jenn Air stainless steel appliances including dual fuel range. Kitchen nook can accommodate a large table. From the nook walk out onto covered patio perfect for relaxing or entertaining. Spacious main level master bedroom has adjoining bath featuring free-standing tub, separate vanities and oversized shower with sleek frameless shower surround. Finished basement has 1 ft. taller ceilings and hosts rec room with wet bar and fireplace, powder bath, three bedrooms and 2 full baths. Two of the lower level bedrooms share a full bath and both have walk-in closets. The third basement bedroom is a junior master suite which hosts a large walk-in closet and ensuite bath. Home comes equipped with a radon mitigation system, smart home package, blown insulation, and AC. Full yard landscaping included!

Stunning 9th floor 2/2 Condo in a 55+ building in the Hillcrest community. This lovely light filled home has breathtaking views of man-made lakes, walking paths, Miami skyline, Hard Rock Guitar Hotel and Stadium. Enjoy the sunset as you lounge on a glass-enclosed balcony. Entertain guests in the living/dining area appointed with ceramic floors and panoramic views. Linger over coffee by the window of the Eat-In Kitchen with its granite counters and backsplashes. Custom double doors lead to a bright guest room with an across the hall bathroom with a step-in shower, granite vanity and lighted mirror. Enjoy the privacy of the owner’s suite with 2 walk-in custom closets plus an en suite bath. Front lot parking. No Rentals. Fiber optic TV, Internet and Smart-controlled lighting and A/C included.
